<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h3>Dear, <%= @user.name %></h3>
    <p> Did you forget your password? </p>
    <br>
    <p>You reset password token is: <b><u><%= @token %></u></b></p>
    <p>This token will expire in 24 hours and can be used only once.</p>
    <br>
    <p>If you don't want to change your password or didn't request this, please ignore and delete this message.</p>
    <br>
    <p>Thank you,</p>
    <p><b>IT Journal Repository Team</b></p>
  </body>
</html>